on \xe2\x80\x94 a man who they said literally would not hurt a fly, choosing instead to set insects free outside. By last Friday morning, investigators had released the suspects\xe2\x80\x99 names \xe2\x80\x94 Tamerlan and Dzhokhar Tsarnaev \xe2\x80\x94 absolving Mr. Tripathi of any connection to the case. Apologies began to pour in to the Tripathi family \xe2\x80\x94 including one from the online forum Reddit , where users had doggedly pursued the rumor \xe2\x80\x94 who began a new social media campaign they hoped would persuade Sunil to come home. The authorities used dental records to identify the body as Mr. Tripathi\xe2\x80\x99s. They did not immediately determine the cause of his death, but said his body had been in the water for some time. \xe2\x80\x9cBe open to letting someone in when it is you who is faltering,\xe2\x80\x9d read the Tripathi family\xe2\x80\x99s statement. \xe2\x80\x9cLend your hand. We need it. The world needs it.\xe2\x80\x9d'
